<section>
	<h3>Template (2021-03-05)</h3>
	<p>Avoid using <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> elements when doing a checklist that doesn't need to be submitted anywhere.</p>
	<p>Notes:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Use the <code>.gc-checklist</code> class on the parent container of the checklist items.</li>
		<li>The <code>&lt;input type="checkbox"&gt;</code> can be use without a parent <code>&lt;form&gt;</code> element.</li>
		<li>Should not be used with other form elements. Only produce a standalone checklist. If other form elements are required, consider building a regular form.</li>
		<li>The feedback message is optional (<code>data-gc-checklist</code>)</li>
	</ul>
